771
00:35:27,686 --> 00:35:30,566
And this is called at some
point after you mark an activity


772
00:35:30,566 --> 00:35:31,656
as needing to be saved.


773
00:35:31,656 --> 00:35:33,046
And we'll call this
method for you


774
00:35:33,176 --> 00:35:34,696
so you can fill in
