834
00:37:56,696 --> 00:37:57,746
or even reboot your machine.


835
00:37:57,746 --> 00:37:59,926
Everything just comes back
exactly the way that it was.


836
00:38:00,926 --> 00:38:06,766
Now, clearly to accomplish
